                            <comment id="13756952" author="hossman" created="Tue, 3 Sep 2013 19:18:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bahg!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That&apos;s terrible .. thanks for reporting this and identifying the fix Catalin.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve attached a patch including Catalin&apos;s fix (along with a bit of refactoring the match) and a fix so that the &quot;reload&quot; test actually tests something useful.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;doing more testing now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
